CoreItemComparison

protected CoreItemComparison(CoreItem olderItem,
                             CoreItem newerItem,
                             boolean deletionChanged,
                             boolean securityChanged)
Constructs a new CoreItemComparison.

Parameters:
olderItem - The older CoreItem in this CoreItemComparison.
newerItem - The newer CoreItem in this CoreItemComparison.
deletionChanged - true if one of the CoreItem versions is marked as deleted while the other is not; false otherwise.
securityChanged - true if the CoreItem versions have different security settings; false otherwise.
